These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian, colombian, argentine, british, indian, thai
7 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, lizard, turtle, guinea-pig, goldfish, pony
 1. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 2. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 3. the thai is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 4. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
 5. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the thai is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
11. the indian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
12. the british is on the left of the indian##1
13. the indian is in the middle##1
14. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
15. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
16. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the thai##6
17. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
18. the owner of the rabbit is not the colombian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | argentine | british | indian | thai | colombian | nigerian |
| Pet           | turtle   | goldfish    | pony       | horse     | lizard    | guinea-pig   | rabbit |

