.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep, salsa, folk, disco, blues, indie
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, dutch, italian, american, spanish, argentine, nigerian
 1. the american is not the fan dubstep##6
 2. the spanish is not the fan dubstep##6
 3. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the fan blues##5
 4. the fan folk is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the italian is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
 6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
 7. the turkish is on the left of the spanish##1
 8. the american is on the left or right of the fan r&b##3
 9. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the fan dubstep##5
10. the spanish is on the right of the fan salsa##1
11. the fan salsa is not the italian##6
12. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
13. the fan salsa is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
14. the fan folk is the argentine##1
15. the spanish is on the left of the fan folk##1
16. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
17. the italian is on the right of the fan folk##1
18. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
19. the fan dubstep is on the right of the fan indie##1
20. the fan blues is on the right of the fan salsa##1
21. the fan blues is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |    5     |   6    |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | blues     | folk     | indie | dubstep      | disco    | r&b |
