.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-4::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, mechanic, writer, videographer, accountant, security-guard, journalist
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, badminton, baseball, soccer, cricket, water-polo, lacrosse
 1. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 4. the firefighter is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is in the middle##1
 6. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 7. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the writer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the security-guard##6
11. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
12. the firefighter is in an even position##4
13. the person who's sport is rugby is not the journalist##6
14. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is rugby and the writer##2
15. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
16. the firefighter is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |      3       |    4    |       5       |         6          |      7      |
| Job     | writer | journalist      | accountant | firefighter  | videographer      | security-guard | mechanic |
| Sport   | water-polo       | soccer | rugby      | cricket | lacrosse | baseball      | badminton    |

