.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-7::.
7 different pets are kept: horse, dog, rabbit, snake, pony, goldfish, rat
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, subway, snowmobile, bus, tram, ship, skateboard
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 3. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 4. the owner of the rat is not the person driving the bus##6
 5. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
 6. the owner of the pony is not the person driving the subway##6
 7. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 8. the person driving the ship is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the rat is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the skateboard##1
12. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
13. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
14. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
15. the owner of the goldfish is not the person driving the ship##6
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |  7   |
| Pet         | pony   | horse       | rat    | snake | dog      | goldfish | rabbit |
| Transport   | bus | subway | car | ship      | snowmobile | tram  | skateboard  |

