The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, documentary, comedy, epic, romance, fantasy
 1. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is not the person watching thriller movies##6
 5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
10. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
11. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person watching thriller movies##2
12. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
13. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
14. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
15. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
16. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
17. the person drinking coffee is the person watching horror movies##1
18. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
