 1. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
 2. the polish is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
 3. the japanese is not the chef##6
 4. the firefighter is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 5. the freelancer is on the left of the engineer##1
 6. the french is on the far right##1
 7. the chef is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 8. the chef is between the pakistani and the japanese##2
 9. the polish is in an even position##4
10. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
11. the spanish is between the software-developer and the firefighter##2
12. the pakistani is on the left or right of the polish##3
13. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
14. the pakistani is the firefighter##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
16. the bartender is on the right of the dutch##1
17. the engineer is on the right of the freelancer##1

